![Lots of Apples Title](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c4cede6eac5360ed2b46dc848f9b688ca6acfcd8.png)

The first thing we wanted to do was get the recipe for the Enchanted Golden Apple back into the game. After that, we decided that it was unfair that there were only golden apples, so we added apples for each ore in Minecraft (each with its own quirks), and some that are not related to ores, but with their special mechanics.


List of Apples:

- Copper Apple;
- Iron Apple;
- Amethyst Apple;
- Emerald Apple;
- Diamond Apple;
- Netherite Apple;
- Glass Apple;
- TNT Apple.


Special Apples:
- Ultimate Apple;
- Infinite Apple.


This is a project created by the Blocksmith Creations team.
